 function and the regularized energy density, showing, moreover,\nthat the outcome is consistent with the standard results of the Casimir effect.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 3 Dec 2014 17:34:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 30 Sep 2015 06:50:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-10-01"}
