ar is X-ray bright with log L_X/L_bol ~= -5.7. The low\nresolution X-ray spectra reveal the presence of a plasma heated up to 24MK. We\nassociate the 24MK plasma in CPD -28 2561 with the presence of a kG strong\nmagnetic field capable to confine stellar wind.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 4 Dec 2014 13:26:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-23"}
